629
00:40:20,212 --> 00:40:22,297
♪ Be our guest, be our guest

630
00:40:22,381 --> 00:40:24,216
♪ Be our guest

631
00:40:25,968 --> 00:40:28,220
♪ Life is so unnerving

632
00:40:28,303 --> 00:40:30,764
♪ For a servant who's not serving

633
