♪ He's not whole
♪ without a soul to wait upon

634
00:40:34,142 --> 00:40:35,644
Get off!

635
00:40:36,478 --> 00:40:37,771
♪ Those good old days

636
00:40:37,813 --> 00:40:39,565
♪ When we were useful

637
00:40:40,732 --> 00:40:44,444
♪ Suddenly, those good old days
♪ are gone

638
00:40:45,153 --> 00:40:47,364
♪ Ten years we've been rusting

639
