664
00:41:41,001 --> 00:41:42,085
♪ And we're obsessed

665
00:41:42,169 --> 00:41:44,004
♪ With your meal, with your ease

666
00:41:44,046 --> 00:41:46,048
♪ Yes, indeed, we aim to please

667
