01:08:11,300 --> 01:08:14,595
I knew it. I knew it was foolish
to get our hopes up.

1001
01:08:14,636 --> 01:08:18,348
Maybe it would have been better
if she'd never come at all.

1002
01:08:18,432 --> 01:08:20,767
-Could it be...
-Is it she?

1003
01:08:20,850 --> 01:08:23,145
Sacrebleu! Invaders!

1004
01:08:23,228 --> 01:08:25,439
-Encroachers.
-And they have the mirror.

1005
01:08:25,522 --> 01:08:26,564
Warn the master.

1006
01:08:26,607 --> 01:08:28,734
If it's a fight they want,
we'll be ready for them.

1007
01:08:28,774 --> 01:08:30,652
Who's with me?

1008
01:08:30,736 --> 01:08:32,738
Take whatever booty you can find.

1009
01:08:32,779 --> 01:08:35,448
But remember, the Beast is mine!

1010
01:08:35,490 --> 01:08:37,451
♪ Hearts ablaze, banners high

1011
01:08:37,492 --> 01:08:39,036
♪ We go marching into battle

1012
01:08:39,118 --> 01:08:41,997
[L]♪ Unafraid, although the danger
[L]♪ just increased

1013
01:08:42,331 --> 01:08:43,874
♪ Raise the flag, sing the song

1014
01:08:43,957 --> 01:08:45,334
♪ Here we come, we're 50 strong

1015
01:08:45,417 --> 01:08:48,587
♪ And 50 Frenchmen can't be wrong

1016
01:08:48,670 --> 01:08:50,421
♪ Let's kill the Beast

1017
01:08:51,173 --> 01:08:53,800
-Pardon me, Master.
-Leave me in peace.

1018
01:08:53,841 --> 01:08:56,303
But, sir, the castle is under attack.

1019
01:08:56,886 --> 01:08:59,473
♪ Kill the Beast! Kill the Beast!

1020
01:08:59,973 --> 01:09:04,310
-This isn't working.
-Lumiere, we must do something!

1021
01:09:04,353 --> 01:09:05,938
Wait! I know!

1022
01:09:06,772 --> 01:09:09,441
♪ Kill the Beast! Kill the Beast!

1023
01:09:10,484 --> 01:09:12,611
What shall we do, Master?

1024
01:09:12,653 --> 01:09:14,821
It doesn't matter now.

1025
01:09:14,863 --> 01:09:16,323
Just let them come.

1026
01:09:16,365 --> 01:09:19,618
♪ Kill the Beast! Kill the Beast!

1027
01:09:19,660 --> 01:09:21,495
♪ Kill the Beast!

1028
01:09:33,881 --> 01:09:34,966
Now!

1029
01:09:55,863 --> 01:09:56,989
Yes!

1030
01:10:00,742 --> 01:10:02,411
Here we go!

1031
01:10:05,914 --> 01:10:07,457
What the devil?

1032
01:10:08,417 --> 01:10:10,043
Belle, look out!

1033
01:10:16,216 --> 01:10:18,510
You guys gotta try this thing.

1034
01:10:23,557 --> 01:10:26,018
Up here, you scurvy scum.

1035
01:10:26,685 --> 01:10:27,978
Now!

1036
01:11:37,631 --> 01:11:39,633
And stay out.

1037
01:12:10,205 --> 01:12:11,415
Get up.

1038
01:12:13,125 --> 01:12:14,334
Get up.

1039
01:12:14,918 --> 01:12:16,920
What's the matter, Beast?

1040
01:12:18,338 --> 01:12:21,258
Too kind and gentle to fight back?

1041
01:12:28,849 --> 01:12:29,850
No!

1042
01:12:33,020 --> 01:12:35,939
-Belle.
-No, Gaston, don't.

1043
01:12:41,904 --> 01:12:43,655
Let's go, Philippe.

1044
01:13:08,722 --> 01:13:10,599
Come on out and fight!

1045
01:13:12,893 --> 01:13:15,812
Were you in love with her, Beast?

1046
01:13:15,896 --> 01:13:18,398
Did you honestly think she'd want you

1047
01:13:18,440 --> 01:13:20,734
when she had someone like me?

1048
01:13:32,412 --> 01:13:36,583
It's over, Beast! Belle is mine!

1049
01:13:41,630 --> 01:13:45,092
Let me go. Let me go.
Please, don't hurt me.

1050
01:13:45,133 --> 01:13:47,261
I'll do anything. Anything!

1051
01:14:01,441 --> 01:14:02,693
Get out.

1052
01:14:04,278 --> 01:14:05,445
Beast!

1053
01:14:06,488 --> 01:14:07,656
Belle.

1054
01:14:16,665 --> 01:14:17,833
Belle?

1055
01:14:23,630 --> 01:14:25,090
You came back.

1056
01:15:04,379 --> 01:15:05,547
You...

1057
01:15:07,090 --> 01:15:08,675
You came back.

1058
01:15:08,717 --> 01:15:12,179
Of course I came back.
I couldn't let them...

1059
01:15:13,055 --> 01:15:14,890
This is all my fault.

1060
01:15:14,973 --> 01:15:16,767
If only I'd gotten here sooner.

1061
01:15:16,850 --> 01:15:21,480
Maybe it's better... It's better this way.

1062
01:15:21,522 --> 01:15:23,982
Don't talk like that.

1063
01:15:24,024 --> 01:15:26,360
You'll be all right.

1064
01:15:26,443 --> 01:15:30,280
We're together now.
Everything's going to be fine, you'll see.

1065
01:15:32,616 --> 01:15:35,702
At least I got to see you

1066
01:15:37,538 --> 01:15:39,039
one last time.

1067
01:15:50,092 --> 01:15:51,802
No. No.

1068
01:15:52,803 --> 01:15:56,765
Please. Please. Please don't leave me.

1069
01:16:00,769 --> 01:16:02,145
I love you.

1070
01:17:41,161 --> 01:17:43,497
Belle, it's me.

1071
01:17:59,513 --> 01:18:00,848
It is you.

1072
01:18:34,214 --> 01:18:35,424
Lumiere.

1073
01:18:36,341 --> 01:18:37,676
Cogsworth.

1074
01:18:39,178 --> 01:18:40,554
Mrs. Potts!

1075
01:18:41,889 --> 01:18:43,974
-Look at us.
-Mama. Mama.

1076
01:18:48,770 --> 01:18:52,274
-Oh, my goodness.
-It is a miracle.

1077
01:19:03,160 --> 01:19:04,411
L'amour.

1078
01:19:08,624 --> 01:19:12,169
Well, Lumiere, old friend.
Shall we let bygones be bygones?

1079
01:19:12,252 --> 01:19:15,088
Of course, mon ami.
I told you she would break the spell.

1080
01:19:15,172 --> 01:19:19,760
I beg your pardon, old friend,
but I believe I told you.

1081
01:19:19,843 --> 01:19:21,637
No, you didn't. I told you.

1082
01:19:21,720 --> 01:19:23,514
You most certainly did not,

1083
01:19:23,597 --> 01:19:25,641
you pompous,
paraffin-headed pea-brain!

1084
01:19:25,724 --> 01:19:28,852
En garde, you overgrown pocket watch!

1085
01:19:28,936 --> 01:19:30,938
-Take that.
-Stop shoving.

1086
01:19:34,274 --> 01:19:37,528
Are they gonna live
happily ever after, Mama?

1087
01:19:37,611 --> 01:19:39,321
Of course, my dear.

1088
01:19:40,197 --> 01:19:41,532
Of course.

1089
01:19:42,366 --> 01:19:45,160
Do I still have to sleep in the cupboard?

1090
01:19:48,622 --> 01:19:52,334
♪ Certain as the sun

1091
01:19:53,585 --> 01:19:56,171
♪ Rising in the east

1092
01:19:56,255 --> 01:19:58,632
♪ Tale as old as time

1093
01:19:58,715 --> 01:20:01,385
♪ Song as old as rhyme

1094
01:20:01,468 --> 01:20:07,307
♪ Beauty and the Beast

1095
01:20:07,432 --> 01:20:10,310
♪ Tale as old as time

1096
01:20:10,352 --> 01:20:13,856
♪ Song as old as rhyme

1097
01:20:13,939 --> 01:20:19,653
♪ Beauty and the Beast
